the Young Turks , has noted the total breakdown in media .","depth":11},{"id":173,"text":"After these scalps","depth":14},{"id":174,"text":"taken by the left-wing mob ,","depth":14},{"id":175,"text":"Tracey said","depth":14},{"id":176,"text":"the \" the media industry is completely f * * ked. \"","depth":14},{"id":177,"text":"He has gone on a tear against the culturally ascendant and total lunatic","depth":16},{"id":178,"text":"left overtaking the activist and media landscapes .","depth":16},{"id":179,"text":"He ' s not wrong .","depth":15},{"id":180,"text":"\" If you ' re an emotionally unstable baby","depth":18},{"id":181,"text":"who regards disagreement as ' violence '","depth":18},{"id":182,"text":"journalism is probably the wrong field for you , \"","depth":17},{"id":183,"text":"he tweeted .","depth":16},{"id":184,"text":"\" Everywhere from the New York Times , to Variety , to The Intercept , these 20 and 30-something journalist cry-bullies are successfully forcing institutions to bend to their will and accommodate their sputtering , logic-free emotional meltdowns . \"","depth":15},{"id":185,"text":"He called them the \" ultimate manipulative gaslighters \" as well .","depth":13},{"id":186,"text":"Granted , Tracey goes after conservative media as well .","depth":12},{"id":187,"text":"He takes aim at both sides ,","depth":12},{"id":188,"text":"and he was one of the few liberal reporters out there","depth":12},{"id":189,"text":"who was even more brutal towards the Trump-Russia collusion hysteria .","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"He added","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"that he wants police reform","depth":11},{"id":192,"text":"but noted","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"that he wants nothing to do with the people at the forefront","depth":13},{"id":194,"text":"of advocating it right now .","depth":13},{"id":195,"text":"I don ' t blame him .","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"Police reform is rapidly devolving into abolishing law enforcement ,","depth":10},{"id":197,"text"